2. hostPath:


As the name indicates this is the bridge/Path between emptyDir and Persistent Volumes (PV)

hostpath vloume it wont create any vloume, just mounts dirctiry or file from kuberentes node to the pod 


Architecture

+------------------------------------+
| Kubernetes Node (Worker Node)      |
|                                    |
| /home/ubuntu/data                  |
|        │                           |
|        │ hostPath                  |
|        ▼                           |
| +------------------------------+   |
| |           Pod                |   |
| |                              |   |
| |  Container                   |   |
| |      │                       |   |
| |      ▼                       |   |
| |    /data                     |   |
| +------------------------------+   |
+------------------------------------+

